# Zigzag matrix filler. Naive...
S   ← 5
P   ← +⨬(¯1_1|1_¯1)◿₂/+.     # Naive predecessor finder.
F‼! ← ⨬(^0|P)^1◿₂/+.◌ °(^2). # Helper macro.

# Fix all the edge cases
Pred ← ⍣(
  0_0 °[0 0]
| F‼!(+0_¯1|∘|⊂0)
| F‼!(+¯1_0|¬|˜⊂0)
| F‼!(+¯1_0|∘|˜⊂(-1S))
| F‼!(+0_¯1|¬|⊂(-1S))
| P
)

Val ← |1 memo(⨬(+1Val Pred|⋅0)≍0_0.)
⍉↯∞_S≡Val⊙◌↯∞_2°⊡˜↯0S_S
